Title: Unplanned
Writer: Abby Johnson (based on the book "Unplanned" by), Chuck Konzelman (screenplay by), Cary Solomon (screenplay by)
Actors: Ashley Bratcher, Brooks Ryan, Robia Scott, Jared Lotz
Plot: All Abby Johnson ever wanted to do was help women. As one of the youngest Planned Parenthood clinic directors in the nation, she believed in a woman's right to choose. Until the day she saw something that changed everything.
